functionalj.lens.lenses

Interface IntegerToLongAccessPrimitive

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AccessCreator<Integer,Long,LongAccess<Integer>>, AnyAccess<Integer,Long>, ComparableAccess<Integer,Long>, Comparator<Integer>, ConcreteAccess<Integer,Long,LongAccess<Integer>>, Func1<Integer,Long>, Function<Integer,Long>, IntFunction<Long>, IntToLongFunction, LongAccess<Integer>, LongAccessPrimitive<Integer>, NumberAccess<Integer,Long,LongAccess<Integer>>, ToLongFunction<Integer>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IntAggregatorToLong
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntAggregatorToLong.Impl
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface IntegerToLongAccessPrimitive
extends LongAccessPrimitive<Integer>, IntToLongFunction, IntFunction<Long>
    Classes implementing this interface know how to access from an int to a long value.
